						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Slab placed in a niche in the courtyard of Paḍaseṭṭi Siddarāmappa's house.</hi></p>						

						<p>12th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This inscription records a gift of land and garden, after purchase, to a temple by the <hi rend="italic">Mahājanas</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Sindige</hi> headed by <hi rend="italic">Ūroḍeya</hi> Sivanātha. In characters of about the <hi rend="bold">12th Century A.D.</hi></p>						

